; FL1 grep-gate arm: no worktree/restore vocabulary anywhere in lib/ —
; comments included; the vocabulary is deleted, not deprecated (README.md
; § design of record vs shipped engine, row 5; fix-forward is a closed
; ruling). grep exits 1 on zero matches — the only accepted exit — so any
; reappearance of the vocabulary in a source or interface file goes red
; with the offending lines in the log.

(rule
 (alias runtest)
 (deps
  (source_tree ../lib))
 (action
  (with-accepted-exit-codes
   1
   (run grep -r -i -E "worktree|restor|rollback" --include=*.ml
     --include=*.mli ../lib))))
